STATE
v.
William Joseph MOORE. No. 460A06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2008. William F.W. Massengale, Chapel Hill, for Moore. Joan Cunningham, Assistant Attorney General, Frank R. Parrish, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 1st day of February 2008 by Defendant for Appropriate Relief:

"Motion Dismissed as Moot by order of the Court in conference this the 11th day of June 2008."
